# Regime-Aware Volatility & Allocation System

A medium-frequency systematic strategy that:
- Detects market regimes using interpretable volatility/trend/drawdown features
- Allocates among SPY, TLT, and BIL based on regime
- Applies volatility targeting + realistic transaction costs
- Avoids look-ahead bias via rebalance timing

## How to run
```bash
python data/download.py
python -c "print('Run notebook or build runner script next')"